content:
Apologies for the confusion in my previous response. You are correct that the CSV file contains information about the cards on the "Projects" list. To answer your question, the cards on the "Projects" list are:

* Personal
* Learn Photoshop
* Learn Stable Diffusion
* Adobe Stock Images
* Create Online Shop

All of these cards have the list name "Projects" and the list ID "62636505e0613831f6703a01" in the CSV file.
